, or are traced as a close contact. From 28 September, <a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-54221953" class="ssrcss-f6h2dj-InlineLink e1kn3p7n0">those who refuse an order to self-isolate could be fined up to £10,000.</a> The new measures also include a one-off support payment of £500 for those on lower incomes. <a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-54214752" class="ssrcss-f6h2dj-InlineLink e1kn3p7n0">The PM is still considering tightening restrictions further</a> after a surge in cases across the UK - another 4,422 cases were recorded on Saturday.</p></div></div><div data-component="image-block" class="ssrcss-xza2yt-ComponentWrapper ep2nwvo1"><figure class="ssrcss-8589xk-StyledFigure e34k3c23"><div class="ssrcss-ab5fd8-StyledFigureContainer e34k3c21"><span class="ssrcss-15ecaci-Placeholder etlorgc0"><span><noscript><picture><source srcSet="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/240/cpsprodpb/17D5D/production/_114492679_optimised-uk_daily_cases_with_ra_19sep-nc.png.webp 240w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/17D5D/production/_114492679_optimised-uk_daily_cases_with_ra_19sep-nc.png.webp 320w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/17D5D/production/_114492679_optimised-uk_daily_cases_with_ra_19sep-nc.png.webp 480w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/17D5D/production/_114492679_optimised-uk_daily_cases_with_ra_19sep-nc.png.webp 624w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/800/cpsprodpb/17D5D/production/_114492679_optimised-uk_daily_cases_with_ra_19sep-nc.png.webp 800w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/976/cpsprodpb/17D5D/production/_114492679_optimised-uk_daily_cases_with_ra_19sep-nc.png.webp 976w" type="image/webp"/><img alt="Chart shows daily cases are continuing to rise" loading="lazy" src="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/2048/cpsprodpb/17D5D/production/_114492679_optimised-uk_daily_cases_with_ra_19sep-nc.png" srcSet="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/240/cpsprodpb/17D5D/production/_114492679_optimised-uk_daily_cases_with_ra_19sep-nc.png 240w, https://ichef.bbci.co.