top entries.</a></p></div></div><div data-component="image-block" class="ssrcss-xza2yt-ComponentWrapper ep2nwvo1"><figure class="ssrcss-8589xk-StyledFigure e34k3c23"><div class="ssrcss-ab5fd8-StyledFigureContainer e34k3c21"><span class="ssrcss-12jfuxk-Placeholder etlorgc0"><span><noscript><picture><source srcSet="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/240/cpsprodpb/BA33/production/_114476674_comp1.jpg.webp 240w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/BA33/production/_114476674_comp1.jpg.webp 320w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/BA33/production/_114476674_comp1.jpg.webp 480w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/BA33/production/_114476674_comp1.jpg.webp 624w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/800/cpsprodpb/BA33/production/_114476674_comp1.jpg.webp 800w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/976/cpsprodpb/BA33/production/_114476674_comp1.jpg.webp 976w" type="image/webp"/><img alt="Winning entry" loading="lazy" src="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/976/cpsprodpb/BA33/production/_114476674_comp1.jpg" srcSet="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/240/cpsprodpb/BA33/production/_114476674_comp1.jpg 240w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/BA33/production/_114476674_comp1.jpg 320w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/BA33/production/_114476674_comp1.jpg 480w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/BA33/production/_114476674_comp1.jpg 624w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/800/cpsprodpb/BA33/production/_114476674_comp1.jpg 800w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/976/cpsprodpb/BA33/production/_114476674_comp1.jpg 976w" width="976" height="650" class="ssrcss-11yxrdo-Image edrdn950"/></picture></noscript></span></span><span role="text" class="ssrcss-tvuve5-StyledFigureCopyright e34k3c20"><span class="visually-hidden ssrcss-1f39n02-VisuallyHidden e16en2lz0">Image source, </span>Jack Crook</span></div></figure></div><div data-component="image-block" class="ssrcss-xza2yt-ComponentWrapper ep2nwvo1"><figure class="ssrcss-8589xk-StyledFigure e34k3c23"><div class="ssrcss-ab5fd