raph e1jhz7w10"><a href="http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/articles/4g8c0mkNmM190Zl00VdXTTb/bbc-news-daily-email" class="ssrcss-f6h2dj-InlineLink e1kn3p7n0">Get a longer coronavirus briefing from the BBC in your inbox, each weekday morning, by signing up here.</a></p></div></div><div data-component="subheadline-block" class="ssrcss-19w8cxh-ComponentWrapper-HeadlineComponentWrapper egtrm1f0"><h2 id="And-dont-forget-" tabindex="-1" class="ssrcss-1ipj56t-Heading e10rt3ze0"><span role="text">And don&#x27;t forget... </span></h2></div><div data-component="text-block" class="ssrcss-uf6wea-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0"><div class="ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1"><p class="ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10">Find more information, advice and guides on our <a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/coronavirus" class="ssrcss-f6h2dj-InlineLink e1kn3p7n0">coronavirus page</a>.</p><p class="ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10">In winter, a blocked or runny nose, a sore throat and a cough are common, so how do you know if you have Covid-19? Check your symptoms <a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/av/health-54182329" class="ssrcss-f6h2dj-InlineLink e1kn3p7n0">here.</a></p></div></div><div data-component="image-block" class="ssrcss-xza2yt-ComponentWrapper ep2nwvo1"><figure class="ssrcss-8589xk-StyledFigure e34k3c23"><div class="ssrcss-ab5fd8-StyledFigureContainer e34k3c21"><span class="ssrcss-4hxohy-Placeholder etlorgc0"><span><noscript><picture><source srcSet="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/240/cpsprodpb/1564D/production/_114492678_uk_corona_figs_19sep_3x-nc.png.webp 240w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/1564D/production/_114492678_uk_corona_figs_19sep_3x-nc.png.webp 320w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/1564D/production/_114492678_uk_corona_figs_19sep_3x-nc.png.webp 480w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/1564D/production/_114492678_uk_corona_figs_19sep_3x-nc.png.webp 624w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/800/cpsprodpb/1564D/production/_1144926